ca.utoronto.utm.paint

类 ShapeStack

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.utoronto.utm.paint.ShapeStack

  • public class ShapeStack
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates a shapeStack model for PaintModel. which holds toDraw Stack, and canceled Stack to store all the shapes to be drawn and canceled,and allows redo and undo to happen.
    作者:
    Mengning Yang and Junwen Shen
